OL,3,CFree speech law for universities being
OL,4,Crevived by government
OL,6,FIn a message to university vice
OL,7,Fchancellors delivered in the House of
OL,8,FCommons, Phillipson warned: "Protect
OL,9,Ffree speech on your campuses, or face
OL,10,Fthe consequences."
OL,12,FThe government confirmed they will
OL,13,Fkeep the duty on universities to
OL,14,F"secure" and "promote the importance"
OL,15,Fof free speech, with a punishment of
OL,16,Fsanctions by the regulator, including
OL,17,Fpossible fines.
