OL,3,CFree speech law for universities being
OL,4,Crevived by government
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIt also included a new complaints
OL,12,Fscheme for students, staff and
OL,13,Fvisiting speakers. The Office for
OL,14,FStudents will be given new powers to
OL,15,Ffine institutions who fail to protect
OL,16,Ffree speech, or even to suspend their
OL,17,Fregistration.
OL,19,FThe government insist the law will
OL,20,Fstill "protect vulnerable groups".
