OL,6,FWhen the law was first introduced,
OL,7,Funiversities also warned it could lead
OL,8,Fto costly legal action as they respond
OL,9,Fto compensation claims and complaints,
OL,10,Fat a time when finances are strapped.
OL,12,FIn an open letter to Phillipson last
OL,13,Fyear, 700 academics warned about
OL,14,Funiversity staff being "hounded,
OL,15,Fcensured, silenced or even sacked".
OL,17,FOne of the most high-profile cases was
OL,18,Fthat of gender-critical Oxford
OL,19,Facademic Kathleen Stock, who resigned
OL,20,Fafter protests and campaigns calling
OL,21,Ffor her dismissal in 2021.
