OL,6,FMany have also criticised the practice
OL,7,Fof "no-platforming" at universities,
OL,8,Fwhere controversial speakers are
OL,9,Funable to appear at events.
OL,11,FTensions on university campuses have
OL,12,Falso risen since the October 7 attacks
OL,13,Fby Hamas in 2023, with a number of
OL,14,Fstudent protests and encampments
OL,15,Fstaged last year across the UK.
